OL,3,CTeenager jailed for life for murdering
OL,4,Cfather of seven
OL,6,FThe teenager was with James
OL,7,FO'Driscoll, 27, in the Ely area of
OL,8,FCardiff on 7 April, 2024, looking to
OL,9,Fconfront Christian Morgan over an
OL,10,Fongoing dispute. Colin Richards, who
OL,11,Fdied as a result, was with Christian
OL,12,FMorgan at the time.
OL,14,FThe court previously heard how the
OL,15,Fviolence had escalated from a
OL,16,Fdisagreement between Christian Morgan,
OL,17,Fa friend of Colin Richards, and the
OL,18,Fother defendants.
