OL,6,FMorgan had received threatening and
OL,7,Finsulting messages from his ex-
OL,8,Fgirlfriend Noreen O'Driscoll, sister
OL,9,Fof James O'Driscoll.
OL,11,FThis culminated in the defendants
OL,12,Fbeing in the area of Heol Berllan on
OL,13,Fthe night of Sunday, 7 April, 2024,
OL,14,Fwhen Mr Richards was fatally injured.
OL,16,FGauci and O'Driscoll were driven to
OL,17,Fthe area by O'Driscoll's mother,
OL,18,FSoraya Somersall where the two men
OL,19,Fconfronted Morgan.
