OL,6,FGauci and O'Driscoll also dumped the
OL,7,Fclothes they had been wearing in a bag
OL,8,Fand left Cardiff. After a three-week
OL,9,Fmanhunt involving several other police
OL,10,Fforces, Gauci and accomplice James
OL,11,FO'Driscoll were arrested in Stoke-on-
OL,12,FTrent, Staffordshire.
OL,14,FColin Richards, 48, from Grangetown,
OL,15,Fdied on 8 April, 2024 as a result of
OL,16,Fhis injury.
