OL,6,FAnthony Clarke of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service said: "Corey Gauci
OL,8,Fand James O'Driscoll had armed
OL,9,Fthemselves and were intent on violence
OL,10,Fwhen they confronted the other men.
OL,12,F"The three women knew what had
OL,13,Foccurred and deliberately tried to
OL,14,Fhide the evidence.
OL,16,F"The brandishing of knives can often
OL,17,Fend with terrible consequences, and
OL,18,Fsadly in this case, it resulted in the
OL,19,Fdevastating loss of life.
