OL,12,Fsaid: "Colin was a much-loved father,
OL,13,Fgrandfather, son, and brother."His
OL,14,Ftragic death has left seven children
OL,15,Fwithout a father, and they continue to
OL,16,Fmiss him greatly. Our thoughts are
